data.title: Refresh QT Framework · Issue #14 · openwrt/video
data.meta_description: Upgrade to 5.15.2 and add Debian patches (https://salsa.debian.org/qt-kde-team/qt/qtbase/-/tree/master/debian/patches) Add serialbus (depend on serialport) Add serialport Refresh libdouble-conversion (move to video feeds ?) Add qt5-sql-m...
